text: Handball Club Kehra is an estonian handball team from Kehra. Their home matches are played at the Kehras Spordihoones. They compete in Meistriliiga and Baltic Handball League. ==Accomplishments== *Baltic Handball League: **Winners (2) : 2011, 2012 *Meistriliiga: **Winners (11) : 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996, 1999, 2003, 2004, 2006, 2009, 2012, 2014 **Runner-Up (8) : 1997, 1998, 2000, 2005, 2008, 2011, 2013, 2015 == Team == === Current squad === :Squad for the 2019–20 season http://www.hckehra.ee/meeskond/ ;Goalkeepers * Mikk Aasmaa * Viktor Nikolajev ;Wingers ;RW: * Uvis Strazdinš ;LW: * Sergio-Silver Kreegimaa * Tanel Vilks * Sigmar Seermann * Marten Mitt ;Line players * Anton Barouski * Mihhail Kašuba * Raiko-Rait Kreegimaa ;Back players ;LB: * David Mamporia * Dmitriy Yankovskiy ;CB: * Vladyslav Naumenko ;RB: * Janar Mägi * Indrek Normak == References == ==External links== * *HC Kehra at eurohandball.com Category:Estonian handball clubs
